uit (White &amp; Pink) – Citrus paradisi</h3><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-291_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Clear, slightly bitter, and activating. Supports focus and a fresh start.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="pf-slide"><div class="sc-leXARK cjZDDT pf-293_" data-pf-type="SlideshowSlide"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-294_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-295_"><img alt="1080x800-Citrat.png__PID:7637905f-dd50-48cd-af7d-e715189eee9c" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x800-Citrat.png?v=1771514673&width=2048" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x800-Citrat.png?v=1771514673&width=375 375w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x800-Citrat.png?v=1771514673&width=550 550w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x800-Citrat.png?v=1771514673&width=768 768w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x800-Citrat.png?v=1771514673&width=1024 1024w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x800-Citrat.png?v=1771514673&width=1280 1280w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x800-Citrat.png?v=1771514673&width=1440 1440w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x800-Citrat.png?v=1771514673&width=1680 1680w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x800-Citrat.png?v=1771514673&width=1800 1800w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x800-Citrat.png?v=1771514673&width=1920 1920w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x800-Citrat.png?v=1771514673&width=2048 2048w" fetchPriority="low" decoding="async" loading="lazy" style="--pf-image-ratio:1.35" width="1080" height="800" sizes="(min-width: 1200px) 33vw, (min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 1199px) 33vw, (min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1024px) 50vw, (max-width: 767px) 75vw" data-pf-type="Image4" class="sc-lmUbDS jhRUAf pf-296_" store="[object Object]"/><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-297_ pf-heading-1-h3">		Cedrat – Citrus medica L. var. vulgaris</h3><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-299_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Ancestral and powerful. Clearly structuring with an archetypal freshness.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="pf-slide"><div class="sc-leXARK cjZDDT pf-301_" data-pf-type="SlideshowSlide"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-302_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-303_"><img alt="1080x800 cabava petitgrain.png__PID:069b5f09-a14d-4432-8522-203ad6b1a6af" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x800_cabava_petitgrain.png?v=1771514700&width=2048" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x800_cabava_petitgrain.png?v=1771514700&width=375 375w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x800_cabava_petitgrain.png?v=1771514700&width=550 550w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x800_cabava_petitgrain.png?v=1771514700&width=768 768w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x800_cabava_petitgrain.png?v=1771514700&width=1024 1024w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x800_cabava_petitgrain.png?v=1771514700&width=1280 1280w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x800_cabava_petitgrain.png?v=1771514700&width=1440 1440w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x800_cabava_petitgrain.png?v=1771514700&width=1680 1680w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x800_cabava_petitgrain.png?v=1771514700&width=1800 1800w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x800_cabava_petitgrain.png?v=1771514700&width=1920 1920w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x800_cabava_petitgrain.png?v=1771514700&width=2048 2048w" fetchPriority="low" decoding="async" loading="lazy" style="--pf-image-ratio:1.35" width="1080" height="800" sizes="(min-width: 1200px) 33vw, (min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 1199px) 33vw, (min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1024px) 50vw, (max-width: 767px) 75vw" data-pf-type="Image4" class="sc-lmUbDS jhRUAf pf-304_" store="[object Object]"/><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-305_ pf-heading-1-h3">		Combava – Citrus hystrix</h3><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-307_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Intense, exotic, and green-spicy. Awakens creativity and sensory awareness.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="pf-slide"><div class="sc-leXARK cjZDDT pf-309_" data-pf-type="SlideshowSlide"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-310_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-311_"><img alt="1080x800 YUZU2.png__PID:22736cd3-a37b-4817-bb87-dadb42edce2d" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x800_YUZU2.png?v=1771591599&width=2048" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x800_YUZU2.png?v=1771591599&width=375 375w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x800_YUZU2.png?v=1771591599&width=550 550w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x800_YUZU2.png?v=1771591599&width=768 768w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x800_YUZU2.png?v=1771591599&width=1024 1024w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x800_YUZU2.png?v=1771591599&width=1280 1280w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x800_YUZU2.png?v=1771591599&width=1440 1440w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x800_YUZU2.png?v=1771591599&width=1680 1680w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x800_YUZU2.png?v=1771591599&width=1800 1800w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x800_YUZU2.png?v=1771591599&width=1920 1920w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x800_YUZU2.png?v=1771591599&width=2048 2048w" fetchPriority="low" decoding="async" loading="lazy" style="--pf-image-ratio:1.35" width="1080" height="800" sizes="(min-width: 1200px) 33vw, (min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 1199px) 33vw, (min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1024px) 50vw, (max-width: 767px) 75vw" data-pf-type="Image4" class="sc-lmUbDS jhRUAf pf-312_" store="[object Object]"/><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-313_ pf-heading-1-h3">		Yuzu – Citrus junos</h3><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-315_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">A Japanese citrus treasure. Refined and complex, positioned between lemon and mandarin. Clarity with gentle depth–nspiring and luminous.</p></div></div></div></div></div><button type="button" style="visibility:hidden" aria-label="Previous" class="pf-slider-prev nav-style-1 "></button><button type="button" style="visibility:hidden" aria-label="Next" class="pf-slider-next nav-style-1 "></button><div class="pf-slider-nav pagination-style-1"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-0c05" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-epRwmx cpmRjY pf-317_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-djVWQC dKziBg"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-318_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-319_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/Pflanzenstrich_blau.png?v=1711454056" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/Pflanzenstrich_blau.png?v=1711454056 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/Pflanzenstrich_blau_1000x.png?v=1711454056 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/Pflanzenstrich_blau_500x.png?v=1711454056 320w" width="3514" height="230" alt="Pflanzenstrich_blau.png__PID:b850d7e1-c00f-4273-9b83-e2ecbfbe7683" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-320_ pf-image-1"/></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-a167" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-epRwmx cpmRjY pf-321_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-djVWQC dKziBg"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-322_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-323_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1500x500_Citrus-flower_leaf_and_orange.png?v=1771594828" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1500x500_Citrus-flower_leaf_and_orange.png?v=1771594828 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1500x500_Citrus-flower_leaf_and_orange_1000x.png?v=1771594828 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1500x500_Citrus-flower_leaf_and_orange_500x.png?v=1771594828 320w" width="1500" height="500" alt="1500x500 Citrus-flower leaf and orange.png__PID:9cdce2a8-38a1-4920-aa4b-07f6c24eede5" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-324_ pf-image-1"/></div></div></div><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-325_ pf-r pf-c-ct pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-326_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-327_ pf-heading-1-h3">Citrus, Expressions of Light, Moving from <br>Leaf to Flower to Fruit</h2><h2 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-329_ pf-heading-1-h3">The bitter orange tree is a true aromatic triad, producing three distinct essential oils from its leaves, flowers, and fruit. Each oil reflects a different stage of the tree’s expression – fresh and green, soft and floral, or bright and citrusy – offering a diverse sensory experience from a single botanical source.</h2><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-331_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">BITTER ORANGE CITRUS TREE –&nbsp;THREE VERY DIFFERENT OILS</p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-752a" data-pf-type="Section" id="pf-a7688fbd--copy-of-RosaDamascena" class="sc-epRwmx cpmRjY pf-333_ pf-color-scheme-1"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-djVWQC dKziBg"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-334_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:8px;--s-sm:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-md:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-335_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1500_grain_citrus.jpg?v=1769773123" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1500_grain_citrus.jpg?v=1769773123 1536w" width="1080" height="1500" alt="1080x1500 grain citrus.jpg__PID:85198af9-418f-4e33-8fb2-6c72d78be7f4" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-336_ pf-image-1"/><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-337_ pf-heading-1-h3"> Leaves And Twigs –&nbsp;Petitgrain</h3><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-339_ pf-heading-1-h3"> Bigarade · Bergamot · Lemon · Combava</h3><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-341_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Petitgrain Bigarade was the original and most traditional Petitgrain, distilled from the leaves and young twigs of Citrus aurantium (bitter orange). The name Bigarade specifically refers to this bitter orange variety. Later, distillation expanded to other citrus species – including Citrus bergamia, Citrus limon, and Citrus hystrix – each offering its own leafy interpretation.Other citrus leaves offer their own character: Bergamot feels elegant and lightly aromatic, Lemon clean and herbaceous, and Combava vivid, intensely leafy, almost electric.These oils shift the citrus story from juicy brightness toward depth and composure. Fresh yet grounding. Expressive yet restrained. A different kind of light – filtered through leaves.</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-md:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-343_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1500_flower_citrus.jpg?v=1769772479" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1500_flower_citrus.jpg?v=1769772479 1536w" width="1080" height="1500" alt="1080x1500 flower citrus.jpg__PID:04770c38-16a2-4ce7-ae84-9f2969e30a9b" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-344_ pf-image-1"/><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-345_ pf-heading-1-h3"> Flower – Neroli</h3><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-347_ pf-heading-1-h3">Bloom of the Bitter Orange Tree</h3><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-349_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">From the ivory blossoms of Citrus aurantium comes Neroli – a radiant expression of citrus in full bloom. Hand-harvested at the peak of flowering and gently steam-distilled, the fragile petals release a luminous floral aroma layered with soft green freshness and a subtle hint of honeyed citrus warmth.Where Petitgrain speaks in green tones, Neroli unfolds in light. Its scent is airy yet intricate, delicately sweet yet refined, embodying both purity and depth in a single breath. Long treasured in fine perfumery and European tradition, Neroli has symbolized grace and serenity for centuries – an aromatic echo of spring mornings, sunlight on petals, and quiet elegance in bloom.</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-md:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-351_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1500_flower_citrus2.2.jpg?v=1771936523" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1500_flower_citrus2.2.jpg?v=1771936523 1536w" width="1080" height="1500" alt="1080x1500 flower citrus2.2.jpg__PID:1ca8e880-010b-43da-b02f-d24f14afa859" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-352_ pf-image-1"/><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-353_ pf-heading-1-h3">Citrus Peel&nbsp;–&nbsp; Radiant Citrus&nbsp;</h3><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-355_ pf-heading-1-h3"> Orange · Bergamot · Lemon · Lime</h3><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-357_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Cold-pressed from the peel of the bitter orange, Citrus aurantium oil reveals citrus in its most vibrant, sunlit form. The rind, rich in aromatic glands, releases an expressive brightness – fresh, lightly bitter, and warmly radiant. It is the fruit’s outer skin that holds this luminous energy, capturing light in liquid form.Other citrus peels reveal their own character: Sweet orange offers rounded warmth and familiarity, bergamot (Citrus bergamia) moves gracefully between sparkling freshness and soft floral depth, lemon (Citrus limon) delivers crisp clarity, and lime (Citrus aurantiifolia) adds vivid, green vitality.&nbsp;Here, citrus is at its most recognizable – bright, expressive, and full of life.&nbsp;</p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-eabd" data-pf-type="Section" id="Oshadhi" class="sc-epRwmx cpmRjY pf-359_ pf-color-scheme-1"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-djVWQC dKziBg"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-360_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-361_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/Pflanzenstrich_blau.png?v=1711454056" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/Pflanzenstrich_blau.png?v=1711454056 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/Pflanzenstrich_blau_1000x.png?v=1711454056 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/Pflanzens