63/5262/files/Pflanzenstrich_blau.png?v=1711454056" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/Pflanzenstrich_blau.png?v=1711454056 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/Pflanzenstrich_blau_1000x.png?v=1711454056 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/Pflanzenstrich_blau_500x.png?v=1711454056 320w" width="3514" height="230" alt="Pflanzenstrich_blau.png__PID:b850d7e1-c00f-4273-9b83-e2ecbfbe7683" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-387_ pf-image-1"/></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-c9a9" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-epRwmx cpmRjY pf-388_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-djVWQC dKziBg"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-389_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-390_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1500x500_Citrus-tumble_from_video.png?v=1771925118" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1500x500_Citrus-tumble_from_video.png?v=1771925118 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1500x500_Citrus-tumble_from_video_1000x.png?v=1771925118 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1500x500_Citrus-tumble_from_video_500x.png?v=1771925118 320w" width="1500" height="500" alt="1500x500 Citrus-tumble from video.png__PID:bc337088-b4af-4fd1-a986-583919c450dd" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-391_ pf-image-1"/></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-0a19" data-pf-type="Section" id="pf-6d629ba5--copy-of-RosaDamascena" class="sc-epRwmx cpmRjY pf-392_ pf-color-scheme-1"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-djVWQC dKziBg"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-393_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-394_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-395_ pf-heading-1-h3">Cold Press Extraction:<br>The&nbsp;Standard for Citrus Oils<br></h2><h2 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-397_ pf-heading-1-h3">Citrus Distillation: The Many Ways to Capture the Citrus Essence</h2></div></div></div><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-399_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-400_"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-401_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:8px;--s-sm:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-402_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-403_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><strong>Cold-press</strong> extraction is the classic, natural method for producing high-quality citrus essential oils. This gentle, heat-free process helps preserve the bright, fresh, and vibrant fragrance that makes citrus oils so beloved in natural cosmetics, fragrances, and wellness-inspired products.The process begins with selecting citrus fruits, often harvested slightly before full ripeness, to preserve the natural aromatic compounds.  </p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-405_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-406_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">The peel contains microscopic oil glands that store the essential oil. The outer peel is mechanically grated, zested, or pressed to release small amounts of natural plant moisture, forming a natural emulsion. The emulsion is then separated by centrifugation to yield pure essential oil. The process helps preserve the bright, fresh, sun-ripened aroma of citrus oils. </p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-408_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-409_"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-410_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:8px;--s-sm:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-md:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-411_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1500_flower_distillation.jpg?v=1772103527" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1500_flower_distillation.jpg?v=1772103527 1536w" width="1080" height="1500" alt="1080x1500 flower distillation.jpg__PID:c6f383f0-647f-4306-a09b-c81b43ab1ba5" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-412_ pf-image-1"/></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:8;--c-md:8;--c-lg:8"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-413_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-414_ pf-heading-2-h3"><strong></strong><strong></strong><strong></strong><first-sel>Tradition Meets Innovation: From Steam to FCF</first-sel></h3><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-416_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Beyond cold-pressed citrus oils, whose brightness comes directly from the fruit’s peel, certain botanicals reveal their character only through the art of distillation.<br> <strong>Traditional distillation </strong>begins with twigs and leaves, where time-honored steam distillation gently releases the plant’s green, herbaceous soul. Through this classic method, the soft freshness of living foliage is preserved–capturing clarity, balance, and the quiet vitality of nature in its pure aromatic form.<br>As the plant becomes more delicate, so must the process. <strong>Gentle Distillation</strong> is reserved for fragile blossoms such as neroli, where low-pressure extraction preserves the most subtle aromatic molecules. This careful approach allows their sweet, luminous citrus-floral elegance to unfold without harshness.&nbsp;<br>From tradition and refinement, we arrive at thoughtful innovation. <strong>Bergamot and the FCF Version </strong>represent a modern evolution of citrus craftsmanship. Unlike many other citrus oils, bergamot is often offered in an FCF (Furocoumarin-Free) version. By carefully removing naturally occurring furocoumarins—compounds that increase photosensitivity—this process preserves the bright, uplifting citrus character while enhancing skin compatibility. The aroma remains vibrant and fresh, yet the oil becomes especially well suited to contemporary cosmetic and fragrance formulations, where radiance and skin comfort go hand in hand.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-8c0a" data-pf-type="Section" id="Production" class="sc-epRwmx cpmRjY pf-418_ pf-color-scheme-1"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-djVWQC dKziBg"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-419_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-420_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/Pflanzenstrich_blau.png?v=1711454056" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/Pflanzenstrich_blau.png?v=1711454056 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/Pflanzenstrich_blau_1000x.png?v=1711454056 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/Pflanzenstrich_blau_500x.png?v=1711454056 320w" width="3514" height="230" alt="Pflanzenstrich_blau.png__PID:b850d7e1-c00f-4273-9b83-e2ecbfbe7683" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-421_ pf-image-1"/></div></div></div><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-422_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-423_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1500x500_Citrus-top_lemons.png?v=1770212110" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1500x500_Citrus-top_lemons.png?v=1770212110 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1500x500_Citrus-top_lemons_1000x.png?v=1770212110 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1500x500_Citrus-top_lemons_500x.png?v=1770212110 320w" width="1500" height="500" alt="1500x500 Citrus-top lemons.png__PID:5d613049-c413-4ae7-80d1-eb727c32f5fe" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-424_ pf-image-1"/><h2 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-425_ pf-heading-1-h3">Why Citrus Is Used All Year
</h2><h2 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-427_ pf-heading-1-h3">Citrus essential oils are often seen as bright and summery–but their true magic is versatility. From the sparkling zest of fruit peels to the green calm of leaves and the soft elegance of blossoms, citrus moves effortlessly through the seasons. Always fresh, never fleeting.
</h2><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-429_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Fresh when you need lightness. Grounding when you need balance. Citrus adapts–through every season.</p><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-431_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:8px;--s-sm:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:3;--c-lg:3"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-432_"><img alt="1080x1080 4 season spring.png__PID:b1350f2a-4044-424c-aef9-f4e26dfae6b8" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_season_spring_51445616-3768-438f-b034-9a3b2933c739.png?v=1770108184&width=2048" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_season_spring_51445616-3768-438f-b034-9a3b2933c739.png?v=1770108184&width=375 375w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_season_spring_51445616-3768-438f-b034-9a3b2933c739.png?v=1770108184&width=550 550w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_season_spring_51445616-3768-438f-b034-9a3b2933c739.png?v=1770108184&width=768 768w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_season_spring_51445616-3768-438f-b034-9a3b2933c739.png?v=1770108184&width=1024 1024w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_season_spring_51445616-3768-438f-b034-9a3b2933c739.png?v=1770108184&width=1280 1280w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_season_spring_51445616-3768-438f-b034-9a3b2933c739.png?v=1770108184&width=1440 1440w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_season_spring_51445616-3768-438f-b034-9a3b2933c739.png?v=1770108184&width=1680 1680w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_season_spring_51445616-3768-438f-b034-9a3b2933c739.png?v=1770108184&width=1800 1800w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_season_spring_51445616-3768-438f-b034-9a3b2933c739.png?v=1770108184&width=1920 1920w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_season_spring_51445616-3768-438f-b034-9a3b2933c739.png?v=1770108184&width=2048 2048w" fetchPriority="low" decoding="async" loading="lazy" style="--pf-image-ratio:1" width="1080" height="1080" sizes="75vw" data-pf-type="Image4" class="sc-lmUbDS jhRUAf pf-433_" store="[object Object]"/><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-434_ pf-heading-2-h3">Spring – Renewal</h3><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-436_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-d17d978a-0084-43b2-9437-4e9aed395652"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Light, green, awakening.Citrus supports moments of transition–when energy begins to rise and clarity returns.</span></p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:3;--c-lg:3"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-439_"><img alt="1080x1080 4 season spring2.png__PID:3ec1266a-e70f-4a99-bcd6-47e8997585e2" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_season_spring2.png?v=1770108153&width=2048" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_season_spring2.png?v=1770108153&width=375 375w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_season_spring2.png?v=1770108153&width=550 550w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_season_spring2.png?v=1770108153&width=768 768w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_season_spring2.png?v=1770108153&width=1024 1024w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_season_spring2.png?v=1770108153&width=1280 1280w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_season_spring2.png?v=1770108153&width=1440 1440w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_season_spring2.png?v=1770108153&width=1680 1680w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_season_spring2.png?v=1770108153&width=1800 1800w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_season_spring2.png?v=1770108153&width=1920 1920w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_season_spring2.png?v=1770108153&width=2048 2048w" fetchPriority="low" decoding="async" loading="lazy" style="--pf-image-ratio:1" width="1080" height="1080" sizes="75vw" data-pf-type="Image4" class="sc-lmUbDS jhRUAf pf-440_" store="[object Object]"/><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-441_ pf-heading-2-h3"> Summer – Freshness</h3><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-443_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-63b21437-4e9a-4d39-9652-76937ea7328c"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Cooling, vibrant, expansive.Perfect for warm days, open windows, and rituals that feel light and alive.</span></p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:3;--c-lg:3"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-446_"><img alt="1080x1080 4 season fall.png__PID:d75a3220-b91d-4023-b95f-7b5e6a086f43" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_season_fall.png?v=1770108120&width=2048" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_season_fall.png?v=1770108120&width=375 375w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_season_fall.png?v=1770108120&width=550 550w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_season_fall.png?v=1770108120&width=768 768w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_season_fall.png?v=1770108120&width=1024 1024w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_season_fall.png?v=1770108120&width=1280 1280w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_season_fall.png?v=1770108120&width=1440 1440w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_season_fall.png?v=1770108120&width=1680 1680w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_season_fall.png?v=1770108120&width=1800 1800w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_season_fall.png?v=1770108120&width=1920 1920w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_season_fall.png?v=1770108120&width=2048 2048w" fetchPriority="low" decoding="async" loading="lazy" style="--pf-image-ratio:1" width="1080" height="1080" sizes="75vw" data-pf-type="Image4" class="sc-lmUbDS jhRUAf pf-447_" store="[object Object]"/><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-448_ pf-heading-2-h3">Autumn – Balance</h3><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-450_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-ed395652-7693-4ea7-b28c-e83c2de1cdeb"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Soft brightness meets grounding warmth.Citrus bridges the shift between activity and rest, freshness and depth.</span></p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:3;--c-lg:3"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-453_"><img alt="1080x1080 4 seasoncold w.png__PID:6ecae6d5-5df8-4832-bb31-42d32b87c289" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_seasoncold_w.png?v=1770108216&width=2048" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_seasoncold_w.png?v=1770108216&width=375 375w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_seasoncold_w.png?v=1770108216&width=550 550w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_seasoncold_w.png?v=1770108216&width=768 768w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_seasoncold_w.png?v=1770108216&width=1024 1024w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_seasoncold_w.png?v=1770108216&width=1280 1280w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_seasoncold_w.png?v=1770108216&width=1440 1440w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_seasoncold_w.png?v=1770108216&width=1680 1680w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_seasoncold_w.png?v=1770108216&width=1800 1800w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_seasoncold_w.png?v=1770108216&width=1920 1920w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_4_seasoncold_w.png?v=1770108216&width=2048 2048w" fetchPriority="low" decoding="async" loading="lazy" style="--pf-image-ratio:1" width="1080" height="1080" sizes="75vw" data-pf-type="Image4" class="sc-lmUbDS jhRUAf pf-454_" store="[object Object]"/><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-455_ pf-heading-2-h3">Winter – Light in the Dark</h3><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-457_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-7ea7328c-e83c-4de1-8deb-5849d8c8b847"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Gentle, uplifting, comforting.When days grow shorter, citrus brings a sense of warmth, clarity, and inner light.</span></p></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-460_ pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-hide"><div class="wrap">
  <div class="col1">
    <img class="img" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/rosenmenge_box.jpg?v=1712219445" width="400" height="400" alt="Centred Image">

    <div class="inner">
      <p>The journey from field to bottle of Rosa Damascena essential oil is a testament to nature's bounty and the
        meticulous craftsmanship required to capture its essence. With awe-inspiring numbers, it's no wonder why this
        precious elixir is highly cherished and revered. To obtain a single kilogram of pure essential oil from Rosa
        Damascena, an astonishing 3,000 to 4,000 kilograms
        of roses are needed. This staggering ratio underscores the remarkable concentration and potency of the oil
        extracted from these delicate blossoms.</br> </br> However, the yield is not solely determined by quantity;
        rather, it is
        influenced by a multitude of factors, including climate, time of harvest, flower quality, and distillation
        techniques. In regions blessed with a mild climate, the conditions are particularly conducive to optimal rose
        cultivation,
        resulting in superior quality and higher yields of essential oil. Furthermore, the bio-rhythms of the roses
        themselves play a pivotal role, dictating the cycles of production of fragrant molecules. This harmonious dance
        between nature's rhythms and human intervention ensures the finest quality oil is obtained.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col2">
    <img class="img" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/rose_quantity_box_engl.jpg?v=1713774067" width="400" height="400" alt="Centred Image">
    <div class="inner">
      <p>The harvesting process is a labor-intensive endeavor, beginning in the early dawn during the revered "Brahma
        muhurta," the Creator's time as per the Vedas. At this auspicious hour, when the world is still draped in the
        quiet embrace of pre-dawn, the roses reach their peak production of essential oil molecules, maximizing potency
        and fragrance.

        And yet, the marvel doesn't end there. To distill just one liter of Rose oil, an astonishing 1,200,000 to
        1,500,000 blossoms must be meticulously hand-picked, one by one. Each small glass of Rose oil, containing
        approximately 30 ml, encapsulates the essence of a staggering 40,000 blossoms. </br> </br> Such concentration is
        further
        highlighted when considering that it takes 50 to 70 Rose blossoms to yield just a single drop of essential oil.

        In essence, every drop of pure Rose oil is a testament to nature's abundance and the profound connection between
        humanity and the natural world. When you apply just one drop of this precious elixir to your heart, you're not
        just indulging in luxury; you're embracing the essence of thousands of blossoms, their beauty, and their wisdom,
        all captured in a single drop.

      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


